---
title: Charred Scallion & Corn Flatbread with Yellow Squash & Salsa Fresca
description: Caramelization is the key to this recipe: developing deep, golden brown color on your corn and scallion creates intense flavor in the final product. Salsa fresca is delicious on more than just tortilla chips - it adds a light, tangy finish to this non-traditional flatbread.
